              Mon-Fri: 8AM-5PM | Emergency: 24/7
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Main Footer Content -->
  <div class="relative z-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-taupe to-charcoal text-soft-white">
    <div class="container-padding max-w-7xl mx-auto py-16">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">

      <!-- Services Column -->
      <div>
